description:
Hudson River Benthic Mapping project.
This data set is a combination of DEC shoreline information from the submerged aquatic vegetation (SAV) project covering the estuary north of Manhattan and NOAA shoreline data for the New York/New Jersey Harbor. From Troy to the north end of Manhattan this shoreline is the same as the file fin_shore83.e00 bundled with the submerged aquatic vegetation files on CUGIR (http://cugir.mannlib.cornell.edu/).  From the north end of Manhattan south, this shoreline file is identical to NOAA's Medium Resolution Digital Vector Shoreline (1998) for the Contiguous United States (http://oceanservice.noaa.gov/dataexplorer/  ftp://spo.nos.noaa.gov/datasets/shoreline/).
